A woman dumped her husband's body in a hole and poured concrete near Belgorod
In Belgorod region, a woman confessed to killing her own husband, whom she dumped in a pit with waste and poured concrete, according to the website of the regional department of the Investigative Committee of the Russian Federation.
It is noted that the suspect had been married to the victim since 1999.
In recent years, her husband began to abuse alcohol and, after another argument, the woman decided to commit murder.
"When her husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his arms and legs, put a plastic bag over his head and pressed him with a pillow.
When her husband stopped showing signs of life, she wrapped her body in a carpet, carried it into the yard, and hid it in a cesspool.
The next day I called a concrete mixer and filled the pit with concrete, "the management said.
Later, the woman reported that her husband had disappeared.
Relatives of the deceased contacted the police, who opened the hole and recovered the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court to arrest the suspect.
The criminal investigation is currently ongoing.
